---
title: Garlic-Butter Chicken Bites on Savoury Rice with Green Beans
description: Pan-fried chicken bites get an elegant French twist with garlic and plenty of butter! And don't worry, any deliciousness that stuck to the pan while cooking the chicken is soaked up by the green beans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garlic-butter-chicken-bites-1d96aa4d.jpg
